This project contains documentation and configuration examples for implementing
BSI IT-Grundschutz compliant QRadar SIEM environments. All examples should be
adapted to specific organizational requirements and tested thoroughly before
production deployment.

The project maintainers are not affiliated with IBM Corporation or the German
Federal Office for Information Security (BSI). IBM QRadar is a trademark of
IBM Corporation. BSI IT-Grundschutz is a standard of the German Federal Office
for Information Security.